channel.title: Zeta Engine MMO CREATOR No Anti - Leech
channel.description:
Ever want to make your own, completely custom, MMORPG?
Well if you do then you have got to see my MMORPG Engine!
Based off of the Eclipse Series, the Zeta Engine is more powerful than ever!
Zeta is a free to use 2D game engine. This game creator makes online mmorpgs. No previous knowledge is necessary because Zeta uses a simple point and click system. If the software does not have the requirements you need you can program it with the source.
If you are new to Zeta looking to quick start your adventures you must open your server before opening your client or else it will say that the server is offline.
Download the Zeta Engine here: *
If you get the runtime error 339 then you have not downloaded the Cache which you can get here: * . (Also learn how to make it run with Vista and Windows 7 here)
Remember, Zeta is a easy to use. But to create a truly fabulous games with this mmorpg maker time and effort will have to be put forward into your masterpiece. Story lines, sprites, graphic interfaces these are all key essences in making the difference between a simple game and a truly unique mmorpg that will go places or generate revenue. The Zeta Game Engine has the capability to create professional games but it takes the user to truly harness that power.
